Fantasy Baseball API Management Service 
- Generate new api key and secrets to use for Fantasy Baseball API

Request
```bash 
curl -X POST https://fantasybaseballapikeymanagementserver.onrender.com/getAPIKey \                 
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"username": "mandytang333", "firstname": "mandy", "lastname": "tang", "email": "tangyue123456@gmail.com"}'

Response 
```
{"keyId":"4a8C1r8UmKGQJCtfNRxvMp","keySecret":"1laxaJH8QMWCRApLf50tzL"}%    
```